 The Good Beach Lagos Nigeria, is set to witness a different and vibrant addition to its line of beach clubs with the launch of The Good Beach. On April 15th 2022, Good Friday, The Good Beach an ultra-modern beach club located at 10b Trinity Avenue Oniru, Victoria Island Lagos, had an exclusive opening as a medium to introduce its new facility to the public. The Good Beach The exceptional venue bursts with a coastal luxury lifestyle, a delightful mix of classic allure and timeless luxury that brilliantly combines the warmth of exquisite cheer, and truly refined comfort. It features various facilities including a blue water glistening pool perfect for swimming, a mini green lawn, private cabanas with splash pools, beachfront cabanas, and 50 loungers by the beachfront. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1729025 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/DSC_1697.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/DSC_1697.jpg 1080w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/DSC_1697-897x598.jpg 897w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/DSC_1697-320x213.jpg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/DSC_1697-640x427.jpg 640w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/DSC_1697-600x400.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> The breathtaking event took place on the private beach club which sits on the beautiful sandy natural waterfront along the Oniru corridor of Victoria Island, Lagos, and treated its guests and beach party enthusiasts a swell time. The Good Beach witnessed different individuals from all works of life who gathered to experience its opening from, DJ Obi, Tosan Wiltshire, Paul O, Sunky O amongst others. Ntosh Gazi performing at The Good Beach Opening South African music artiste Ntosh Gazi also thrilled the guests with some amampiano sounds and some South African dance styles. Hosted by lagos finest hypeman Aksmuth, alongside reknown DJ Factor on set, the event kicked off with the best selection of music for guests who had the opportunity to explore various fun activities while been treated to mouth watering culinary delicacies, and sipping on classic and signature cocktails. It was indeed a memorable experience. The Good Beach is the perfect place for those seeking a mind-body reset, total relaxation and the joy of a luxurious lifestyle experience. About The Good Beach Located on the premier beachfront gliding across the Atlantic coastline in the heart of Victoria Island Lagos. The Good Beach is an ultra-trendy beach club far away from the chaotic scene of the city of Lagos. The Good Beach is a great place to enjoy the ocean breeze, white beach sand, a calm and peaceful atmosphere, cool ocean breeze, and an azure blue sky. The food, experiences, and ambiance of this new-age beach reflects the soul of ‘Ibiza’: free-spirited, curious, and wild which it is highly inspired by. Your lifestyle is carefully tailored for you to explore, enjoy and indulge in an authentic and opulent voyage experience at The Good Beach. If you’re planning a large gathering of family or friends, a special event, or looking to have a Balearic beach experience, then The Good Beach might just be the perfect destination. It’s a place to go crazy and get loose. For more information regarding the restaurant and the launch of Vendome please visit (@thegoodbeachlagos) on Instagram. See more photos from the event: